data.title: Honor Roll of Donors
data.text:
The Honor Roll of Donors contains names of individuals who have made gifts to the University of Georgia that were processed through the Office of Development between July 1, 2021 and June 30, 2022. There could be several reasons that your name does not appear in what you believe to be the appropriate giving levelâ€”or not appear at all:

You made your qualifying gift after June 30, 2022.

You gave more before June 30, 2022, than you realize; your name may be in the next giving level.

You made a pledge instead of an outright gift; this list reflects gifts received.

Your planned gift is not documented by the UGA Foundation, or you have withdrawn your planned gift between July 1, 2021, and June 30, 2022.
